      <h1 class="text-2xl sm:text-4xl font-extrabold text-white leading-tight">Your OOS Defines the Rules. Your Runtime Enforces Them. You Need Both.</h1>
      <p class="text-gray-400 mt-4 text-base sm:text-lg leading-relaxed">Why the architecture layer and the monitoring layer are complementary, not competing -- and what happens when you have one without the other.</p>
